OL,3,CInvestigation after man dies in police
OL,4,Cvan
OL,6,FAn investigation has been launched by
OL,7,Fthe police watchdog after a man died
OL,8,Fin a police van following an incident
OL,9,Fat a cinema.
OL,11,FThe Independent Office for Police
OL,12,FConduct (IOPC) said Lancashire Police
OL,13,Fofficers were called to reports of a
OL,14,Fman refusing to leave the cinema at
OL,15,FHolmes Mill in Clitheroe just before
OL,16,Fmidnight on 11 July.
