OL,3,CInvestigation after man dies in police
OL,4,Cvan
OL,6,FOfficers detained the man, in his 30s,
OL,7,Funder Section 136 of the Mental Health
OL,8,FAct and a decision was then made to
OL,9,Ftransport him in a police van to Royal
OL,10,FBlackburn Hospital.
OL,12,FThe IOPC said man's condition
OL,13,Fdeteriorated further at the hospital
OL,14,Fand he was placed in the back of a
OL,15,Fpolice van while it was parked in an
OL,16,Fambulance bay at the A&E department,
OL,17,Fwith checks carried out by officers.
