OL,6,FAfter he became unresponsive, medical
OL,7,Fstaff began CPR and tried to
OL,8,Fresuscitate him for about an hour
OL,9,Fbefore a clinical decision was made to
OL,10,Fcease and he was declared dead.
OL,12,FIn a statement, a spokesperson from
OL,13,Fthe IOPC said: "Through our enquiries,
OL,14,Fwe understand a woman spoke to the man
OL,15,Fat the Holmes Mill Complex prior to
OL,16,Fthe police arriving and that members
OL,17,Fof the public inside A&E witnessed the
OL,18,Fcontact police had with the man while
OL,19,Fat the hospital. We believe these
OL,20,Fpeople will be able to assist with our
OL,21,Fenquiries.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
