OL,6,F"Following a mandatory referral from
OL,7,Fthe force we declared an independent
OL,8,Finvestigation at 10.25am on Saturday
OL,9,F12 July. IOPC investigators attended
OL,10,Fthe post incident procedures to begin
OL,11,Fgathering evidence."
OL,13,FIOPC Director Amanda Rowe said: "Our
OL,14,Fthoughts are with the man's family and
OL,15,Ffriends, and all those affected by his
OL,16,Fdeath. We have now met with his family
OL,17,Fto explain our role and have advised
OL,18,Fthem of the next steps.
