OL,4,Cvan
OL,6,FA Lancashire Police spokesperson said:
OL,7,F"We can confirm we have referred this
OL,8,Fmatter to the Independent Office for
OL,9,FPolice Conduct and that they are
OL,10,Findependently investigating. For that
OL,11,Freason, it would be inappropriate to
OL,12,Fcomment any further at this stage
OL,13,Fother than to say our thoughts are
OL,14,Fwith the loved ones of the man who
OL,15,Fsadly died and that we will, of
OL,16,Fcourse, continue to cooperate fully
OL,17,Fwith the IOPC."
